fern.network.sbml
Class MathTree

java.lang.Object
  fern.network.sbml.MathTree

public class MathTree
extends Object

Representation of am evaluation tree. Within a sbml file, MathML branches may occur at different positions. These are represented as MathTrees in FERN.

Author:
Florian Erhard
